## Installation

### Barrel

```ts
import { LayerCard, LayerCardPrimary, LayerCardSecondary } from "kumo-svelte";
```

### Granular

```ts
import { LayerCard, LayerCardPrimary, LayerCardSecondary } from "kumo-svelte/components/layer-card";
```

## Usage

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import { LayerCard, LayerCardPrimary, LayerCardSecondary } from "kumo-svelte";
</script>

<LayerCard layered class="w-[250px]">
  <LayerCardSecondary>Documentation</LayerCardSecondary>
  <LayerCardPrimary>Learn how to use Kumo components</LayerCardPrimary>
</LayerCard>
```

LayerCard also supports a simple surface-style mode for cases where you do not need a secondary header row. In those cases, render content directly inside `LayerCard` and omit the `layered` prop.

```svelte
<LayerCard class="w-[250px] p-4">
  Learn how to use Kumo components
</LayerCard>
```

